software.leonov.common.util.function

Interface CheckedLongUnaryOperator

  • Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface CheckedLongUnaryOperator
    Mirror of the LongUnaryOperator interface whose applyAsLong(long) method can throw a checked exception.
